27/01/2008
BRDO, Slovenia -- Romania and Bulgaria signed a declaration for their accession to the Schengen common border control and visa space on Friday (January 25th).
According to the document, the two countries aim to become full-right members of the Schengen system by March 2011.
(Makfax, A1 - 26/01/08;
Insurance.bg, Netinfo, Rompres - 25/01/08)
